Package superkidsapplication.providers

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ImageProvider
    The ImageProvider allows access to image icons through the use of a key.
    MusicProvider
    The MusicProvider allows access to music files through a key.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FilePathImageProvider
    The FilePathImageProvider serves up images through the use of a key-value pair that maps the image key to a file path of the image.
    FilePathMusicProvider
    The FilePathMusicProvider serves up the audio streams by using a key-value pair for the path to the piece of music.
    ResourceProviderFactory
    The ResourceProviderFactory provides access to resource providers used by the UI elements.
